title: BRIEF-Diana Containerships Announces Direct Continuation Of Time Charter Contract
text:
February 1, 2018 / 2:25 PM / in 9 minutes BRIEF-Diana Containerships Announces Direct Continuation Of Time Charter Contract Reuters Staff 
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Diana Containerships Inc: 
* DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS INC. ANNOUNCES DIRECT CONTINUATION OF TIME CHARTER CONTRACT FOR M/V SAGITTA WITH HAPAG-LLOYD 
* DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS INC - GROSS CHARTER RATE IS US$8,400 PER DAY, MINUS A 1.25% COMMISSION PAID TO THIRD PARTIES 
* DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS INC - NEW CHARTER PERIOD WILL COMMENCE ON FEBRUARY 15, 2018 
* DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS INC - GROSS CHARTER RATE PAID TO THIRD PARTIES, FOR A PERIOD OF MINIMUM THREE MONTHS TO MAXIMUM FIVE MONTH Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
